We got above error, because defined google resource defined in main.tf, "demo-bucket" is referencing gcs_bucket_name default= "terraform-demo-terra-bucket" was already exist in my GCS account. It needs to be unique.

I changed it to new name as below:

variable "gcs_bucket_name" {
  description = "My Storage Bucket Name"
  #Update the below to a unique bucket name
  default     = "preproject-gcs-bucket"
}

